'''声景'''是指人类感知的[[声音|声音]]环境。最初由Michael Southworth在1967年提出<ref>{{cite journal |title=The Sonic Environment of Cities |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_environment-and-behavior_1969-06_1_1/page/49 |journal=Environment and Behavior |date=1969-06 |volume=1 |issue=1 |pages=49–70 |doi=10.1177/001391656900100104}}</ref>, 主要应用于[[城市规划|城市规划]]、[[建筑设计|建筑设计]]、音乐[[作曲|作曲]]等领域<ref name="biods.2020114">{{cite journal |last1=Zhao |first1=Ying |last2=Shen |first2=Xiaoli |last3=Li |first3=Sheng |last4=Zhang |first4=Yanyun |last5=Peng |first5=Renhua |last6=Ma |first6=Keping |title=Progress and outlook for soundscape ecology |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-07-20 |volume=28 |issue=7 |pages=806 |doi=10.17520/biods.2020114}}</ref>。

根据声音来源的不同，声景分为[[生物声音|生物声音]]、[[物理环境声音|物理环境声音]]和[[人造声音|人造声音]]<ref name="biods.2020114" />。

